					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can probably have 16kB of RAM from $6000-$7ffff, and mirror the top 7kB into $4400-$5fff, so that you have a power of 2 amount.  Just by having a lot of RAM in bank $00 would speed up code a lot because you wouldn't need long addressing as much, you can use the DP and SP more, you can use PEA and PEI more.<br /><br />Also, with fast RAM, you can also make use of self-modifying code.</div>

